OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry and clear with some patchy
OL,7,Ffrost. Clouding over from the south in
OL,8,Fthe early hours with some showery rain
OL,9,Fspreading into the southwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FSome showery rain spreading
OL,12,Fnorth in the morning otherwise dry.
OL,13,FRather cloudy but some bright spells
OL,14,Fmay break through at times. Very mild.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,17,Fspreading east on Thursday afternoon,
OL,18,Fclearing the east early on Friday.
OL,19,FThen Friday and Saturday will be dry
OL,20,Fwith some brightness.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
